{"tid":1973434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內媒稱哈薩克想回歸中國 哈薩克召見大使抗議","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:54:57.000Z","uid":154277,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad0ea4533b34b8a3c0e9025a14fc1aa05c0daad","tid":1973434,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"近日，中國網站上面流傳一篇標題名為「哈薩克斯坦為何渴望回歸中國？」嘅文章，聲稱「哈薩克渴望成為中國一部份」，內容仲話哈薩克「歷來都是中國領土的一部分」，表示哈薩克人對於被中國不斷入侵一事，「並未有太多抱怨」。哈薩克認為呢件事罕有，召見中國大使表達抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國係咪見自己嘅外交同外宣衰L曬，所以另起爐灶玩「老屈式統一」？但寫還寫，內文方面真係要俾啲心機去寫囉，寫到人哋被中國不斷入侵都無乜抱怨，咁誇張邊有人信㗎～0分！重作！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.636202799852077/1689814321157581/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fofficialchapmanto%2Fphotos%2Fa.636202799852077%2F1689814321157581%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=14550198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/officialchapmanto/photos/a.636202799852077/1689814321157581/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"495a360d074608e7e920ebd5ea53399149f97ccc","tid":1973434,"uid":54085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqtFuGg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqtFuGg.jpg&h=03c589a4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}